<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.10">
<l>vēṭṭattaik karutā taṭiyiṇai vaṇaṅki meymmainiṉ ṟemperu māṉai</l>
<l>vāṭṭiṟal tāṉai maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ māṉavēl kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ</l>
<l>tōṭṭalar paintārc cuṭarmuṭi yāṉaip  paḻamoḻi yālpaṇin turaitta</l>
<l>pāṭṭivai pāṭap pattimai perukic cittamum tiruvoṭu mikumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [you] sing these songs which recount old adages, remaining true,</l>
<l rend="indent">grasping the two feet of our lord,</l>
<l>Without thinking of [worldly] desires, worshipping him</l>
<l rend="indent">with a bright crown of fresh garlands of clustered flowers,</l>
<l>These poems of Kaliyaṉ with a proud spear, leader of those of Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with a strong army with swords,</l>
<l>Increasing [your] devotion, intellect and prosperity will multiply.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
